{"tid":1745605,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人不在，票在 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:08:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51c19f28eb62c0ba77a9d8b0a3445162ed9bb25e","tid":1745605,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191122/20810941/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F20810941%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylopVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=1412cfb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F20810941%2F&h=e694bd2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191122/20810941/</a><br />\n<br />\n人不在，票在 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191122/large/1574317387_4cf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191122%2Flarge%2F1574317387_4cf4.jpg&h=cb712379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果，曾鈺成去到將軍澳知專劈頭問的是：「陳彥霖喺咪呢度？」陳彥霖不會離奇由活生生15歲年輕人變成赤裸裸的魔鬼山浮屍。<br />\n<br />\n如果，曾鈺成在將軍澳停車場劈頭問操普通話的黑警的是：「科大周梓樂喺咪呢度？」周梓樂不會無緣無故從停車場三樓墮落二樓，不尋常地沒有任何骨折但頭爆盆骨碎裂，與特區政權同年生、同年亡。<br />\n<br />\n看着快要出生的孩子，選擇救火救人與救香港的消防員方志雄，不獲准保釋，沒法到產房，更加沒辦法這個星期日去投票。<br />\n<br />\n我們，沒有如果。無機會多等陳彥霖3年，沒機會讓符合選民投票年齡的周梓樂走向票站，無機會叫法庭讓方志雄行使他的公民投票權。人不在，票在。念念莫忘，一票傳心，替他們投。<br />\n<br />\n（執筆時新聞指廉署警告，收起長者身份證妨礙投票者屬違法。頂！老人院次次係咁收，將老人掌心雷一車車送去屠房咁，老廉毋須效忠PK鄧，心繫的不是721黑社會！霹靂拉人吧！） <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"9787baf6d9071fcd10864c376750406b72f9eaa3","tid":1745605,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"【抗爭者區議會免責宣示】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745587</a>"},{"pid":"d557303c06f53ccc0eafe63bf6dcffa5b9d083ad","tid":1745605,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"1124一定要全民都投建制派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745329</a>"}]}